== 开发 ==
2010年3月1日，「《[[生化危机系列|生化危机]]》之父」[[三上真司|三上真司]]与12人在[[大阪市|大阪]]开设了游戏开发工作室：{{le|探戈游戏工作室|Tango Gameworks}}（Tango Gameworks）；工作室其後遷移至[[东京|东京]]<ref>[http://www.polygon.com/features/2014/2/20/5425802/shinji-mikami-the-evil-within SHINJI MIKAMI AND THE FOUNTAIN OF YOUTH] {{Wayback|url=http://www.polygon.com/features/2014/2/20/5425802/shinji-mikami-the-evil-within |date=20210307225239 }}.Polygon.2014-02-20.[2015-01-04].</ref>。《恶灵附身》是该工作室正式开发的第一款游戏，於2010年末以《Project Zwei》（Zwei是[[德语|德语]]“二”）为开发代号<ref name="EuroGMikami">{{cite web|first=Robert|last=Purchese|url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2012-04-27-resi-creator-extremely-confident-about-new-game-zweis-graphics|title=Resi creator "extremely confident" about new game Zwei's graphics|publisher=[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]]|date=2012-04-27|accessdate=2014-09-06|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6SOR1EGYK?url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2012-04-27-resi-creator-extremely-confident-about-new-game-zweis-graphics|archivedate=2014-09-06|deadurl=no}}</ref>、以工作室修改过的[[id_Tech_5|id Tech 5]][[遊戲引擎|引擎]]开发<ref name="PolygonE3"/><ref name="IGNApril13">{{cite web |last=Goldfarb |first=Andrew |url=http://uk.ign.com/articles/2013/04/19/shinji-mikamis-new-game-is-the-evil-within |title=Shinji Mikami's New Game is The Evil Within |publisher=[[IGN|IGN]] |date=2013-04-19 |accessdate=2013-04-20 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6SOUVQ0Vp?url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2013/04/19/shinji-mikamis-new-game-is-the-evil-within |archivedate=2014-09-06 |deadurl=no }}</ref>，由三上真司担任总监督<ref name="PolygonE3">{{cite web| first =Michael| last =McWhertor| url =http://www.polygon.com/a/e3-2014/the-evil-within| title =The Evil Within mixes survival horror with psychological terror, then steeps it in gore| publisher =[[Polygon_(website)|Polygon]]| date =2014| accessdate =2014-09-06| archiveurl =https://www.webcitation.org/6SOLOsI7N?url=http://www.polygon.com/a/e3-2014/the-evil-within| archivedate =2014-09-06| deadurl =no}}</ref><ref name="EuroGZRating">{{cite web|first=Tom|last=Phillips|url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2014-07-08-japanese-gamers-must-download-dlc-to-get-the-evil-withins-uncensored-version|title=Japanese gamers must download DLC to get The Evil Within's uncensored version|publisher=[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]]|date=2014-07-08|accessdate=2014-09-06|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6SOTlbCHT?url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2014-07-08-japanese-gamers-must-download-dlc-to-get-the-evil-withins-uncensored-version|archivedate=2014-09-06|deadurl=no}}</ref><ref name="JoystiqApril13">{{cite web |last=Gilbert |first=Ben |date=2012-04-25 |url=http://www.joystiq.com/2012/04/25/resident-evils-mikami-welcomes-bethesda-to-the-world-of-surviva/ |title=Resident Evil's Mikami welcomes Bethesda to the world of survival horror |publisher=[[Joystiq|Joystiq]] |accessdate=2013-04-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130408091352/http://www.joystiq.com/2012/04/25/resident-evils-mikami-welcomes-bethesda-to-the-world-of-surviva/ |archive-date=2013-04-08 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。工作室在开发工作開始後不久被[[美国|美国]]媒体集团[[ZeniMax_Media|ZeniMax Media]]收购成为游戏公司[[贝塞斯达软件|贝塞斯达软件]]的子公司<ref name="EuroGZwei">{{cite web|first=Wesley|last=Yin-Poole|url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2012-04-25-resident-evil-creators-new-game-is-a-survival-horror-codenamed-zwei|title=Resident Evil creator's new game is a survival horror codenamed Zwei|publisher=[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]]|date=2012-04-25|accessdate=2014-09-06|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6SOQqVuqu?url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2012-04-25-resident-evil-creators-new-game-is-a-survival-horror-codenamed-zwei|archivedate=2014-09-06|deadurl=no}}</ref>。

三上真司表示他有感現代恐怖遊戲著重動作而非求生而希望制作一款生存恐怖游戏<ref name="EuroGHorror">{{cite web|first=Tom|last=Phillips|url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2013-04-22-resident-evil-creator-survival-horror-isnt-scary-anymore|title=Resident Evil creator Mikami: "There aren't any real survival horror games in the world right now"|publisher=[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]]|date=2013-04-22|accessdate=2014-09-06|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6SOT0iEWg?url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2013-04-22-resident-evil-creator-survival-horror-isnt-scary-anymore|archivedate=2014-09-06|deadurl=no}}</ref>。針對恐怖遊戲橋段日益容易預測，《恶灵附身》故意让劇情发生在封闭空间内、限制弹药數量和使敌人接近無敵，使玩家感到弱小无力并促使玩家在面對敵人时選擇逃走而非迎戰，從而使遊戲更合乎生存恐怖游戏的类型和主题<ref name="Edge">{{cite web|url=http://www.edge-online.com/features/shinji-mikami-the-father-of-survival-horror-bringing-fresh-terror-to-games/|title=Father of survival horror Shinji Mikami promises fresh terror with The Evil Within|publisher=[[Future_plc|Future plc]]|work=[[Edge_(magazine)|Edge]]|date=2013-12-05|accessdate=2014-09-06|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6SOYwmSbC?url=http://www.edge-online.com/features/shinji-mikami-the-father-of-survival-horror-bringing-fresh-terror-to-games/|archivedate=2014-09-06|deadurl=no}}</ref>。艺术监督片貝直紀表示遊戲內被铁丝网缠住和被插着玻璃碎片的敌人是遭受恶灵之苦的受害者；精神医院的靈感來源是美国[[加州|加州]]的鬼屋[[溫徹斯特神祕屋|溫徹斯特神祕屋]]<ref name="IGNFirstLook">{{cite web|last=O'Brien|first=Lucy|url=http://uk.ign.com/articles/2013/04/22/the-evil-within-first-look|title=The Evil Within - First Look|publisher=[[IGN|IGN]]|date=2013-04-22|accessdate=2014-09-06|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6SOaEC5qI?url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2013/04/22/the-evil-within-first-look|archivedate=2014-09-06|deadurl=no}}</ref>。

貝塞斯達軟件自2013年4月15日起公開一系列遊戲宣傳片段<ref name="PCGamerApril13">{{cite web |last=Wylde |first=Tyler |date=2013-04-16 |url=http://www.pcgamer.com/2013/04/16/bethesda-vine-teaser/ |title=Bethesda tweets cryptic Vine video, says "guess again" to Fallout 4 rumors |publisher=PC Gamer |accessdate=2013-04-20 |archive-date=2014-07-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140713075104/http://www.pcgamer.com/2013/04/16/bethesda-vine-teaser/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，其後在同月19日正式公開遊戲名稱、對應主機平台和即場試玩用家反應短片<ref name="IGNApril13"/>，更多短片分別在同年9月17日<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Z4WqOQTxisM |title=存档副本 |access-date=2015-02-13 |archive-date=2021-01-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210107203655/http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Z4WqOQTxisM |dead-url=no }}</ref>和9月27日公開<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=H1POefYUgkw#t=13 |title=存档副本 |access-date=2015-02-13 |archive-date=2021-02-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210202231403/http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=H1POefYUgkw#t=13 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2014年9月25日，貝塞斯達軟件宣佈遊戲進入[[軟件版本週期|完成版]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gamespot.com/articles/the-evil-within-goes-gold-ahead-of-october-launch/1100-6422553/|title=The Evil Within Goes Gold Ahead of October Launch|publisher=Gamespot|date=2014-09-25|accessdate=2014-09-26|archive-date=2020-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111202134/https://www.gamespot.com/articles/the-evil-within-goes-gold-ahead-of-october-launch/1100-6422553/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

