== 發行 ==
遊戲在2014年10月發行<ref name="KotakuRelease">{{cite web |last=Nakamura |first=Toshi |date=2013-04-25 |url=http://kotaku.com/the-evil-within-will-be-more-about-using-your-brain-tha-480580900 |title=The Evil Within Will Be More About Using Your Brain Than Your Gun |publisher=[[Kotaku|Kotaku]] |accessdate=2013-04-25 |archive-date=2013-05-27 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6Gv8SsgWf?url=http://kotaku.com/the-evil-within-will-be-more-about-using-your-brain-tha-480580900 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="PolygonRelease">{{cite web |last=Lien |first=Tracey |date=2013-05-28 |url=http://www.polygon.com/2013/5/28/4363210/the-evil-withins-first-15-minutes-sets-a-spooky-and-suspenseful-tone |title=The Evil Within's first 15 minutes sets a spooky and suspenseful tone |publisher=[[Polygon_(website)|Polygon]] |accessdate=2013-09-13 |archive-date=2021-11-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211128173242/https://www.polygon.com/2013/5/28/4363210/the-evil-withins-first-15-minutes-sets-a-spooky-and-suspenseful-tone |dead-url=no }}</ref>，在[[日本|日本]]發行的版本名為《Psycho Break》<ref name="EuroGAnnounce">{{cite web|first=Tom|last=Phillips|url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2013-04-19-shinji-mikamis-the-evil-within-announced-for-cross-gen-2014-release|title=Shinji Mikami's The Evil Within announced for cross-gen, 2014 release|publisher=[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]]|date=2013-04-19|accessdate=2014-09-06|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6SOKRNkWb?url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2013-04-19-shinji-mikamis-the-evil-within-announced-for-cross-gen-2014-release|archivedate=2014-09-06|deadurl=no}}</ref>。日本版本刪去了過分血腥的內容以通過當地評審，讓年滿十七歲或以上人士購買，但相關內容可透過[[追加下載內容|追加下載內容]]获得<ref name="EuroGZRating"/>。

作為遊戲推廣，[[澳洲|澳洲]][[黃金海岸_(澳大利亞)|黃金海岸]]之[[華納兄弟電影世界|華納兄弟電影世界]]在其年度活動「Fright Nights」中建造了一個迷宮，內有遊戲中出現之人物角色<ref name="AusGMovieWorld">{{cite web|url=http://www.ausgamers.com/news/read/3470218/the-evil-within-becomes-a-real-horror-story-thanks-to-warner-bros-movie-world|title=The Evil Within Becomes a Real Horror Story thanks to Warner Bros. Movie World|publisher=[[AusGamers|AusGamers]]|date=2014-09-04|accessdate=2014-09-06|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6SOU9ry3H?url=http://www.ausgamers.com/news/read/3470218/the-evil-within-becomes-a-real-horror-story-thanks-to-warner-bros-movie-world|archivedate=2014-09-06|deadurl=no}}</ref>。2014年10月14日，[[黑馬漫畫|黑馬漫畫]]發行了「邪靈入侵的藝術」（The Art of the Evil Within），公開了遊戲的[[概念藝術|概念藝術]]和製作花絮<ref name="IGNArt">{{cite web|last=Schedeen|first=Jesse|url=http://uk.ign.com/articles/2014/08/20/exclusive-the-art-of-the-evil-within-hc-preview|title=Exclusive: The Art Of The Evil Within Hc Preview|publisher=[[IGN|IGN]]|date=2014-08-20|accessdate=2014-09-06|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6SOUSvD4N?url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2014/08/20/exclusive-the-art-of-the-evil-within-hc-preview|archivedate=2014-09-06|deadurl=no}}</ref>。

== 追加下載內容 ==
遊戲設有追加下載內容，可使用角色分別為潔曼和頭目敵人「管理員」（The Keeper）。潔曼的追加下載內容將有新劇情、敵人和地點，以探索主劇情內的迷團為核心；管理員的追加下載內容將以完成殺敵目標為核心<ref name="PolygonDLC">{{cite web| first =Alexa| last =Ray Corriea| url =http://www.polygon.com/2014/8/13/5998227/the-evil-within-season-pass| title =The Evil Within's season pass will let you play as one of its bloodiest enemies| publisher =[[Polygon_(website)|Polygon]]| date =2014-08-13| accessdate =2014-09-06| archiveurl =https://www.webcitation.org/6SOOOqFhY?url=http://www.polygon.com/2014/8/13/5998227/the-evil-within-season-pass| archivedate =2014-09-06| deadurl =no}}</ref>。

